{"type":"message","id":"e9c9e9c4","parentId":"9eff166d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:45:51.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No memory results. I need to produce a report based on the task description. Since there's no existing data, I'll provide a structured framework/template response within 200 characters as requested. Let me keep it concise and actionable.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**5A订单管理汇报**（框架性建议，需结合实际数据填充）\n\n1. **状态盘点框架**：建立看板按\"黄(剩余<3天)/红(逾期)\"分级监控，目标按时完成率≥99%，异常单≤3%，预警单逐日递减。\n2. **Q2产能**：50单在手+预计新增约30单，单人负荷偏紧。建议引入兼职助理或优化审批流转降耗时。\n3. **SOP优化建议**：①材料预审前置至签约时减少反复补件；②关键节点设自动提醒防遗漏；③模板库标准化常用地勘/环评文件。\n4. **售后交接时效**：办结后24小时内完成归档并移交6号，7日内完成首通回访确认客户满意度，形成闭环记录。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":16284,"output":280,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16564,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757547715,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5d4d85b0-2fa2-9bae-b53a-a07db9ecb064"}}
